    <SectionHeading eyebrow="Contact" title="Open to research, platform, and applied medical AI conversations." />
    <div class="story-card rounded-lg p-7">
      <p class="text-lg leading-8 text-slate-300">
        The fastest way to reach me is by email or LinkedIn. I am open to conversations around medical AI, imaging workflows, research software, and scalable ML systems.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-3">
        <a class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 p-4 font-semibold text-white transition hover:border-cyan/45" href="mailto:ajugeorge93@gmail.com">ajugeorge93@gmail.com</a>
        <a class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 p-4 font-semibold text-white transition hover:border-cyan/45" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/aju-george-216501106/">LinkedIn</a>
        <a class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 p-4 font-semibold text-white transition hover:border-cyan/45" href="https://ajugeorge97.github.io/">Personal site</a>
      </div>
    </div>
